6&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562767&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562768&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562769&amp;quot;:6}"&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Capture processes&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;​&lt;br&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;Think aloud,&amp;nbsp;self-assessment checklists or surveys, learning logs, individual or pair conferences,&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;or teacher observations&lt;/span&gt;​&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li data-aria-posinset="4" role="listitem" data-aria-level="1"&gt;&lt;p xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" paraid="0" paraeid="{1382163c-d459-4adf-9586-87ed6d3b79b9}{89}" data-ccp-props="{&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559683&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:240,&amp;quot;335559731&amp;quot;:-230,&amp;quot;335559737&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562764&amp;quot;:2,&amp;quot;335562765&amp;quot;:1.13999,&amp;quot;335562766&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562767&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562768&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562769&amp;quot;:6}"&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Use&amp;nbsp;choice boards&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;​&lt;br&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;Choice boards organize options in a consistent way to support learner autonomy while&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;providing consistent access to choices&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;Go back to the&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="$@COURSEVIEWBYID*291@$#section-5" target="_blank"&gt;Try It Yourself Section&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;for a list of all Try it Yourself Options.&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="@@PLUGINFILE@@/divider-wave-1.png" alt="" width="1920" height="195" role="presentation" class="img-responsive atto_image_button_text-bottom"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</content>
